## Design Philosophy

- Modern Minimalism, Dark-First, Glass Morphism, Gradient Accents, Consistent Spacing (8px grid)

## Color System

### Core Backgrounds & Surfaces (Dark-first)

- **Backgrounds**:
  - `bg-gray-900` (primary page background)
  - `bg-gray-800/50`, `bg-gray-800/60`, `bg-gray-800/70`, `bg-gray-800/90` (cards, overlays)
  - Gradients: `bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900`
- **Surfaces & Borders**:
  - Borders: `border-gray-700/50`, `border-gray-600`, `ring-1 ring-gray-700/50`
  - Muted fills: `bg-gray-700/50`, `bg-gray-700`
- **Text**:
  - Default: `text-white`
  - Secondary: `text-gray-400`
  - Muted: `text-gray-500`
  - Subtle labels: `text-gray-300`

### Accent Palette

- **Indigo (Primary accent)**:
  - Solids: `indigo-600` (default), `indigo-700` (hover)
  - Text: `text-indigo-500` (primary typographic and icon accent)
  - Focus/selection: prefer `ring-indigo-500/20`, `ring-indigo-500/30`, `ring-indigo-500/50`, `border-indigo-500/50`
- **Blue (Secondary/legacy accent, gradients, links)**:
  - Solids: `blue-600` (default), `blue-700` (hover)
  - Text: `text-blue-400` (links, minor accents)
  - Focus/selection: `ring-blue-500/20`, `ring-blue-500/30`, `ring-blue-500/50`, `border-blue-500/50`
- **Purple (Secondary gradient accent)**:
  - Solids: `purple-600` (paired in gradients), `purple-700` (hover)
  - Text: `text-purple-400` (secondary accent text)

### Feedback & Status Colors

- **Error/Destructive**: `red-400`, `red-500`, `red-600`, `red-700`
  - Inputs: `border-red-500`, `focus:ring-red-500/20`
  - Toasts: `bg-red-600 text-white`
- **Success**: `text-green-500` (Typography only; no dedicated success components found)

### Gradients

- **Primary gradient**: `from-blue-600 to-purple-600`
  - Buttons, progress fills, primary CTAs
- **Soft accent backgrounds**: `from-blue-600/20 to-purple-600/20`
  - Accent cards, selected states, icon tiles

## Interaction States

### Buttons (`src/components/ui/Button`)

- **Primary**: `bg-indigo-600 text-white` â†’ hover `bg-indigo-700`; shadows may use subtle indigo glow
- **Secondary**: `bg-gray-700 text-white` â†’ hover `bg-gray-800`
- **Outline**: `border-gray-600 text-white` â†’ hover `bg-gray-700`
- **Ghost**: `text-blue-600` â†’ hover `bg-blue-500/10` (dark-friendly hover)
- **Gradient**: `bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600` â†’ hover `from-blue-700 to-purple-700`
- **Focus**: prefer `focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500/50` where applicable
- **Active**: scale down `active:scale-95`
- **Disabled**: `disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed`

### Inputs (`src/components/ui/Input` and form fields)

- Base: `border-gray-600 bg-gray-700/50 text-white`
- Placeholder: `placeholder:text-gray-400`
- **Focus**: `focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-blue-500/20`
- **Error**: `border-red-500 focus:border-red-500 focus:ring-red-500/20`

### Selectable Pills/Cards (recommendation steps)

- Base: `border-gray-700/50 bg-gray-800/50`
- Hover: `hover:border-gray-600/50`
- Focus: `ring-2 ring-blue-500/50`
- Selected: `border-blue-500/50 ring-blue-500/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/20 to-purple-600/20`

### Progress & Indicators

- Progress bar fill: `bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-purple-600`
- Active step: `bg-blue-500 ring-2 ring-blue-500/20`

### Toasts

- Default: `bg-white text-gray-700 border-gray-300`
- Destructive: `bg-red-600 text-white`
- Actions: focus rings `focus:ring-gray-400`; destructive variants `focus:ring-red-400`

